        to return ``True`` from your local_command_line() implementation to
        suppress the default handling. See
        `gapplication-example-cmdline2.c <https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/glib/-/blob/HEAD/gio/tests/gapplication-example-cmdline2.c>`_
