    ``/org/gtk/Debugging`` on the bus given as
    :attr:`Gio.DebugControllerDBus.connection` once itŌĆÖs initialized. The
    object will be unregistered when the last reference to the
    :class:`Gio.DebugControllerDBus` is dropped.

    This D-Bus object can be used by remote processes to enable or disable debug
    output in this process. Remote processes calling
    ``org.gtk.Debugging.SetDebugEnabled()`` will affect the value of
    :attr:`Gio.DebugController.debug-enabled` and, by default,
    :func:`GLib.log_get_debug_enabled`.

