        Stop the session bus started by :meth:`Gio.TestDBus.up`.

        Unlike :meth:`Gio.TestDBus.down`, this won't verify the :class:`Gio.DBusConnection`
        singleton returned by :func:`Gio.bus_get` or :func:`Gio.bus_get_sync` is destroyed. Unit
